data.title: October 2015 – Tatamagouche Area Singers
data.meta_description: 1 post published by Tatamagouche Area Singers during October 2015
data.text: Welcome all to the official website of the Tatamagouche Area Singers. A choral group consisting of women, men, boys and girls, singing in SATB. We sing many genres of music during the Christmas and Spring seasons, and have been asked to take part in a number of other musical events throughout the year. Take a minute to browse our site, see what we are all about. We are always welcoming new singers, and if you are interested in joining us, please come on out… we would LOVE to have you!
